///   </li>
///   <li>
///     <em>Superimposed mode</em>: the view fills a target view and dragging is disabled.
///   </li>
/// </ul>
/// When dragging ends, the view automatically snaps to the nearest corner.
/// The view respects safe area insets and configurable margins when computing
/// valid positions.
